Program Version 1.0 30/12/2015

General Usage Notes:

This is a game where you can learn how to use different words to form a sentence.

You can also learn how appropriately words can be placed in a sentence.

The word that you provide is placed in a complex sentence.
 
Enter your word and hit "Go!" to witness the magic.You will find your word placed in a complex sentence.

You should enter some meaninful words such that you will get a meaningful sentence.

Different sentences will be generated for the same key word.

